# Detector constraints

- Classical image processing only (see `CONTEXT.md` allowed techniques).
- Do **not** add OCR, trained models, or cloud vision APIs.
- Do **not** use dataset folder / class name inside detection logic.
- Crops must come from the original frame (`pdiseg.pipeline.crop_and_save`).

When suggesting improvements, prefer masks, scoring, morphology — not deep learning.
